## File Reference

| File | Written by | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `01-raw-idea.md` | You (optional) | Your free-text feature idea |
| `02-spec.md` | Composer → Caveman | Lean technical spec |
| `02-claw-input.md` | Composer (fallback) | Full prompt for manual Claw paste |
| `03-opus-plan.md` | Claw/Opus | Step-by-step implementation plan |
| `04-implementation-log.md` | Composer | Per-step progress log |

---

## Model Reference

| Flag | Claw model string | Use when |
|---|---|---|
| `--model opus` | `claude-opus-4-6` | Complex logic, novel architecture, many edge cases |
| `--model sonnet` | `claude-sonnet-4-5` | Most features — good balance of cost and quality |
| `--model haiku` | `claude-haiku-4-5` | Simple, well-defined tasks with clear spec |

